  "title": "createFeature",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/store/src/feature_creator.ts?message=docs(store)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L29-L110\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/13.0.2/modules/store/src/feature_creator.ts#L29-L110\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/store\", \"name\": \"@ngrx/store\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/store/createFeature\", \"name\": \"createFeature\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/store\">@ngrx/store</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"createfeature\">createFeature<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/store/createFeature#createfeature\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A function that accepts a feature name and a feature reducer, and creates\na feature selector and a selector for each feature state property.</p>\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/store/createFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">createFeature</a></span>&#x3C;AppState extends Record&#x3C;string, any>, FeatureName extends keyof AppState &#x26; string = keyof AppState &#x26; string, FeatureState extends AppState[FeatureName] = AppState[FeatureName]>(featureConfig: <a href=\"api/store/FeatureConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">FeatureConfig</a>&#x3C;FeatureName, FeatureState> &#x26; NotAllowedFeatureStateCheck&#x3C;FeatureState>): Feature&#x3C;AppState, FeatureName, FeatureState></code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>featureConfig</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>An object that contains a feature name and a feature reducer.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>Feature&#x3C;AppState, FeatureName, FeatureState></code>: An object that contains a feature name, a feature reducer,\na feature selector, and a selector for each feature state property.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/store/createFeature#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p><strong>With Application State</strong></p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\ninterface AppState {\n  products: ProductsState;\n}\n\ninterface ProductsState {\n  products: Product[];\n  selectedId: string | null;\n}\n\nconst initialState: ProductsState = {\n  products: [],\n  selectedId: null,\n};\n\n// AppState is passed as a generic argument\nconst productsFeature = <a href=\"api/store/createFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">createFeature</a>&#x3C;AppState>({\n  name: 'products',\n  reducer: <a href=\"api/store/createReducer\" class=\"code-anchor\">createReducer</a>(\n    initialState,\n    <a href=\"api/store/on\" class=\"code-anchor\">on</a>(ProductsApiActions.loadSuccess(<a href=\"api/store-devtools/StoreDevtools#state\" class=\"code-anchor\">state</a>, { products }) => ({\n      ...state,\n      products,\n    }),\n  ),\n});\n\nconst {\n  selectProductsState, // type: <a href=\"api/store/MemoizedSelector\" class=\"code-anchor\">MemoizedSelector</a>&#x3C;AppState, ProductsState>\n  selectProducts, // type: <a href=\"api/store/MemoizedSelector\" class=\"code-anchor\">MemoizedSelector</a>&#x3C;AppState, Product[]>\n  selectSelectedId, // type: <a href=\"api/store/MemoizedSelector\" class=\"code-anchor\">MemoizedSelector</a>&#x3C;AppState, string | null>\n} = productsFeature;\n</code-example>\n<p><strong>Without Application State</strong></p>\n<code-example language=\"ts\">\nconst productsFeature = <a href=\"api/store/createFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">createFeature</a>({\n  name: 'products',\n  reducer: <a href=\"api/store/createReducer\" class=\"code-anchor\">createReducer</a>(initialState),\n});\n\nconst {\n  selectProductsState, // type: <a href=\"api/store/MemoizedSelector\" class=\"code-anchor\">MemoizedSelector</a>&#x3C;Record&#x3C;string, any>, ProductsState>\n  selectProducts, // type: <a href=\"api/store/MemoizedSelector\" class=\"code-anchor\">MemoizedSelector</a>&#x3C;Record&#x3C;string, any>, Product[]>\n  selectSelectedId, // type: <a href=\"api/store/MemoizedSelector\" class=\"code-anchor\">MemoizedSelector</a>&#x3C;Record&#x3C;string, any, string | null>\n} = productsFeature;\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/store\n - guide/store/feature-creators\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/store\n - api/store-devtools/StoreDevtools#state\n - api/store/FeatureConfig\n - api/store/MemoizedSelector\n - api/store/createFeature#createfeature\n - api/store/createFeature#usage-notes\n - api/store/createReducer\n - api/store/on\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/store/src/feature_creator.ts?message=docs(store)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L29-L110\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/13.0.2/modules/store/src/feature_creator.ts#L29-L110\n-->"
